             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am an officer: I went with Curtis to the puppet-show and took the prisoner; we carried her to the 
               <persName id="t17770409-5-person47">
                  Brown
                   Bear
               <interp inst="t17770409-5-person47" type="surname" value="Bear"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770409-5-person47" type="given" value="Brown"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770409-5-person47" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             in Bow-street; there I stripped her and took the things mentioned in the indictment from her.</p>
               <p>[They were produced in Court, and deposed to by the prosecutrix.]</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I lived in that house before, it is a house that takes in girls to go out of a night.</p>
               <p>
